{"tha-ap503:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap503:0.2":"Kanikaravagga ","tha-ap503:0.3":"1 Tikanikarapupphiyattheraapadana ","tha-ap503:1.1":"“Sumedho nama sambuddho, ","tha-ap503:1.2":"battimsavaralakkhano; ","tha-ap503:1.3":"Vivekakamo sambuddho, ","tha-ap503:1.4":"himavantamupagamim. ","tha-ap503:2.1":"Ajjhogayha himavantam, ","tha-ap503:2.2":"aggo karuniko muni; ","tha-ap503:2.3":"Pallankamabhujitvana, ","tha-ap503:2.4":"nisidi purisuttamo. ","tha-ap503:3.1":"Vijjadharo tada asim, ","tha-ap503:3.2":"antalikkhacaro aham; ","tha-ap503:3.3":"Tisulam sukatam gayha, ","tha-ap503:3.4":"gacchami ambare tada. ","tha-ap503:4.1":"Pabbatagge yatha aggi, ","tha-ap503:4.2":"punnamayeva candima; ","tha-ap503:4.3":"Vane obhasate buddho, ","tha-ap503:4.4":"salarajava phullito. ","tha-ap503:5.1":"Vanagga nikkhamitvana, ","tha-ap503:5.2":"buddharamsibhidhavare; ","tha-ap503:5.3":"Nalaggivannasankasa, ","tha-ap503:5.4":"disva cittam pasadayim. ","tha-ap503:6.1":"Vicinam addasam puppham, ","tha-ap503:6.2":"kanikaram devagandhikam; ","tha-ap503:6.3":"Tini pupphani adaya, ","tha-ap503:6.4":"buddhasetthamapujayim. ","tha-ap503:7.1":"Buddhassa anubhavena, ","tha-ap503:7.2":"tini pupphani me tada; ","tha-ap503:7.3":"Uddhamvanta adhopatta, ","tha-ap503:7.4":"chayam kubbanti satthuno. ","tha-ap503:8.1":"Tena kammena sukatena, ","tha-ap503:8.2":"cetanapanidhihi ca; ","tha-ap503:8.3":"Jahitva manusam deham, ","tha-ap503:8.4":"tavatimsamagacchaham. ","tha-ap503:9.1":"Tattha me sukatam byamham, ","tha-ap503:9.2":"kanikariti nayati; ","tha-ap503:9.3":"Satthiyojanamubbedham, ","tha-ap503:9.4":"timsayojanavitthatam. ","tha-ap503:10.1":"Sahassakandam satabhendu, ","tha-ap503:10.2":"dhajaluharitamayam; ","tha-ap503:10.3":"Satasahassaniyyuha, ","tha-ap503:10.4":"byamhe patubhavimsu me. ","tha-ap503:11.1":"Sonnamaya manimaya, ","tha-ap503:11.2":"lohitangamayapi ca; ","tha-ap503:11.3":"Phalikapi ca pallanka, ","tha-ap503:11.4":"yenicchaka yadicchaka. ","tha-ap503:12.1":"Maharahanca sayanam, ","tha-ap503:12.2":"tulikavikatiyutam; ","tha-ap503:12.3":"Uddhalomikaekantam, ","tha-ap503:12.4":"bibbohanasamayutam. ","tha-ap503:13.1":"Bhavana nikkhamitvana, ","tha-ap503:13.2":"caranto devacarikam; ","tha-ap503:13.3":"Yada icchami gamanam, ","tha-ap503:13.4":"devasanghapurakkhato. ","tha-ap503:14.1":"Pupphassa hettha titthami, ","tha-ap503:14.2":"uparicchadanam mama; ","tha-ap503:14.3":"Samanta yojanasatam, ","tha-ap503:14.4":"kanikarehi chaditam. ","tha-ap503:15.1":"Satthituriyasahassani, ","tha-ap503:15.2":"sayam patamupatthahum; ","tha-ap503:15.3":"Parivarenti mam niccam, ","tha-ap503:15.4":"rattindivamatandita. ","tha-ap503:16.1":"Tattha naccehi gitehi, ","tha-ap503:16.2":"talehi vaditehi ca; ","tha-ap503:16.3":"Ramami khiddaratiya, ","tha-ap503:16.4":"modami kamakamiham. ","tha-ap503:17.1":"Tattha bhutva pivitva ca, ","tha-ap503:17.2":"modami tidase tada; ","tha-ap503:17.3":"Nariganehi sahito, ","tha-ap503:17.4":"modami byamhamuttame. ","tha-ap503:18.1":"Satanam pancakkhattunca, ","tha-ap503:18.2":"devarajjamakarayim; ","tha-ap503:18.3":"Satanam tinikkhattunca, ","tha-ap503:18.4":"cakkavatti ahosaham; ","tha-ap503:18.5":"Padesarajjam vipulam, ","tha-ap503:18.6":"gananato asankhiyam. ","tha-ap503:19.1":"Bhavabhave samsaranto, ","tha-ap503:19.2":"mahabhogam labhamaham; ","tha-ap503:19.3":"Bhoge me unata natthi, ","tha-ap503:19.4":"buddhapujayidam phalam. ","tha-ap503:20.1":"Duve bhave samsarami, ","tha-ap503:20.2":"devatte atha manuse; ","tha-ap503:20.3":"Annam gatim na janami, ","tha-ap503:20.4":"buddhapujayidam phalam. ","tha-ap503:21.1":"Duve kule pajayami, ","tha-ap503:21.2":"khattiye capi brahmane; ","tha-ap503:21.3":"Nice kule na jayami, ","tha-ap503:21.4":"buddhapujayidam phalam. ","tha-ap503:22.1":"Hatthiyanam assayanam, ","tha-ap503:22.2":"sivikam sandamanikam; ","tha-ap503:22.3":"Labhami sabbamevetam, ","tha-ap503:22.4":"buddhapujayidam phalam. ","tha-ap503:23.1":"Dasiganam dasaganam, ","tha-ap503:23.2":"nariyo samalankata; ","tha-ap503:23.3":"Labhami sabbamevetam, ","tha-ap503:23.4":"buddhapujayidam phalam. ","tha-ap503:24.1":"Koseyyakambaliyani, ","tha-ap503:24.2":"khomakappasikani ca; ","tha-ap503:24.3":"Labhami sabbamevetam, ","tha-ap503:24.4":"buddhapujayidam phalam. ","tha-ap503:25.1":"Navavattham navaphalam, ","tha-ap503:25.2":"navaggarasabhojanam; ","tha-ap503:25.3":"Labhami sabbamevetam, ","tha-ap503:25.4":"buddhapujayidam phalam. ","tha-ap503:26.1":"Imam khada imam bhunja, ","tha-ap503:26.2":"imamhi sayane saya; ","tha-ap503:26.3":"Labhami sabbamevetam, ","tha-ap503:26.4":"buddhapujayidam phalam. ","tha-ap503:27.1":"Sabbattha pujito homi, ","tha-ap503:27.2":"yaso abbhuggato mama; ","tha-ap503:27.3":"Mahapakkho sada homi, ","tha-ap503:27.4":"abhejjapariso sada; ","tha-ap503:27.5":"Natinam uttamo homi, ","tha-ap503:27.6":"buddhapujayidam phalam. ","tha-ap503:28.1":"Sitam unham na janami, ","tha-ap503:28.2":"parilaho na vijjati; ","tha-ap503:28.3":"Atho cetasikam dukkham, ","tha-ap503:28.4":"hadaye me na vijjati. ","tha-ap503:29.1":"Suvannavanno hutvana, ","tha-ap503:29.2":"samsarami bhavabhave; ","tha-ap503:29.3":"Vevanniyam na janami, ","tha-ap503:29.4":"buddhapujayidam phalam. ","tha-ap503:30.1":"Devaloka cavitvana, ","tha-ap503:30.2":"sukkamulena codito; ","tha-ap503:30.3":"Savatthiyam pure jato, ","tha-ap503:30.4":"mahasale suaddhake. ","tha-ap503:31.1":"Panca kamagune hitva, ","tha-ap503:31.2":"pabbajim anagariyam; ","tha-ap503:31.3":"Jatiya sattavassoham, ","tha-ap503:31.4":"arahattamapapunim. ","tha-ap503:32.1":"Upasampadayi buddho, ","tha-ap503:32.2":"gunamannaya cakkhuma; ","tha-ap503:32.3":"Taruno pujaniyoham, ","tha-ap503:32.4":"buddhapujayidam phalam. ","tha-ap503:33.1":"Dibbacakkhu visuddham me, ","tha-ap503:33.2":"samadhikusalo aham; ","tha-ap503:33.3":"Abhinnaparamippatto, ","tha-ap503:33.4":"buddhapujayidam phalam. ","tha-ap503:34.1":"Patisambhida anuppatto, ","tha-ap503:34.2":"iddhipadesu kovido; ","tha-ap503:34.3":"Dhammesu paramippatto, ","tha-ap503:34.4":"buddhapujayidam phalam. ","tha-ap503:35.1":"Timsakappasahassamhi, ","tha-ap503:35.2":"yam buddhamabhipujayim; ","tha-ap503:35.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap503:35.4":"buddhapujayidam phalam. ","tha-ap503:36.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","tha-ap503:36.2":"bhava sabbe samuhata; ","tha-ap503:36.3":"Nagova bandhanam chetva, ","tha-ap503:36.4":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap503:37.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","tha-ap503:37.2":"mama buddhassa santike; ","tha-ap503:37.3":"Tisso vijja anuppatta, ","tha-ap503:37.4":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","tha-ap503:38.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap503:38.2":"vimokkhapi ca atthime; ","tha-ap503:38.3":"Chalabhinna sacchikata, ","tha-ap503:38.4":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap503:39.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma tikanikarapupphiyo thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap503:40.1":"Tikanikarapupphiyattherassapadanam pathamam. "}